### ============================================
### 🧪 TEST REPORTS API - SuperMarketMini
### ============================================

@baseUrl = http://localhost:5000
@adminToken = 
@managerToken = 

### ============================================
### 🔐 1. LOGIN (Chạy trước để lấy token)
### ============================================

### 1.1 Login Admin
# @name loginAdmin
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "admin",
  "password": "Admin@123"
}

### 1.2 Login Manager
# @name loginManager
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "manager",
  "password": "Manager@123"
}

### ============================================
### 📊 2. DAILY SALES REPORT
### ============================================

### 2.1 Admin - Daily Sales Default (Last 7 days) (Expected: 200 OK)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/reports/sales/daily
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### 2.2 Admin - Daily Sales with Date Range (Expected: 200 OK)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/reports/sales/daily?fromDate=2024-01-01&toDate=2024-01-31
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### 2.3 Admin - Daily Sales Invalid Range (Expected: 400 Bad Request)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/reports/sales/daily?fromDate=2024-12-31&toDate=2024-01-01
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### 2.4 Manager - Daily Sales (Expected: 200 OK)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/reports/sales/daily
Authorization: Bearer {{managerToken}}

### ============================================
### 📈 3. MONTHLY SALES REPORT
### ============================================

### 3.1 Admin - Monthly Sales Default (Current Year) (Expected: 200 OK)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/reports/sales/monthly
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### 3.2 Admin - Monthly Sales Specific Year (Expected: 200 OK)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/reports/sales/monthly?year=2024
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### 3.3 Manager - Monthly Sales (Expected: 200 OK)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/reports/sales/monthly
Authorization: Bearer {{managerToken}}

### ============================================
### 🏆 4. TOP SELLING PRODUCTS
### ============================================

### 4.1 Admin - Top Selling Default (Last 30 days, Top 10) (Expected: 200 OK)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/reports/products/top-selling
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### 4.2 Admin - Top Selling with Date Range (Expected: 200 OK)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/reports/products/top-selling?fromDate=2024-01-01&toDate=2024-12-31
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### 4.3 Admin - Top Selling Custom Top (Expected: 200 OK)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/reports/products/top-selling?top=5
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### 4.4 Admin - Top Selling Top 20 (Expected: 200 OK)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/reports/products/top-selling?top=20
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### ============================================
### 📂 5. SALES BY CATEGORY
### ============================================

### 5.1 Admin - Sales by Category Default (Expected: 200 OK)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/reports/sales/by-category
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### 5.2 Admin - Sales by Category with Date Range (Expected: 200 OK)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/reports/sales/by-category?fromDate=2024-01-01&toDate=2024-12-31
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### 5.3 Manager - Sales by Category (Expected: 200 OK)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/reports/sales/by-category
Authorization: Bearer {{managerToken}}

### ============================================
### 📦 6. INVENTORY REPORT
### ============================================

### 6.1 Admin - Inventory Summary (Expected: 200 OK)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/reports/inventory/summary
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### 6.2 Manager - Inventory Summary (Expected: 200 OK)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/reports/inventory/summary
Authorization: Bearer {{managerToken}}

### ============================================
### 👥 7. TOP CUSTOMERS REPORT
### ============================================

### 7.1 Admin - Top Customers Default (Last 90 days, Top 10) (Expected: 200 OK)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/reports/customers/top
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### 7.2 Admin - Top Customers with Date Range (Expected: 200 OK)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/reports/customers/top?fromDate=2024-01-01&toDate=2024-12-31
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### 7.3 Admin - Top Customers Custom Count (Expected: 200 OK)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/reports/customers/top?top=5
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### ============================================
### 🎯 8. DASHBOARD REPORT
### ============================================

### 8.1 Admin - Dashboard Overview (Expected: 200 OK)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/reports/dashboard
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### 8.2 Manager - Dashboard Overview (Expected: 200 OK)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/reports/dashboard
Authorization: Bearer {{managerToken}}

### ============================================
### ❌ 9. UNAUTHORIZED ACCESS
### ============================================

### 9.1 No Token - Dashboard (Expected: 401 Unauthorized)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/reports/dashboard

### 9.2 No Token - Daily Sales (Expected: 401 Unauthorized)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/reports/sales/daily

### ============================================
### 📝 HƯỚNG DẪN SỬ DỤNG
### ============================================
### 
### 1. Cài đặt VS Code extension "REST Client"
### 2. Chạy các request Login đầu tiên để lấy token
### 3. Copy token vào biến tương ứng
### 4. Chạy các request test theo thứ tự
###
